		{ heading: `You meet the love you’re called to imitate — as Father`, bodyHtml: `Ephesians tells you to love like Christ. The Father’s Heart Bible™ reveals God as <em>Father</em> wherever Scripture does — from <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read/genesis/1" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">Genesis 1</a> onward — so you don’t just study a standard, you stand under a Father’s love and learn to give what you’ve received.` },
		{ heading: `It refills the man before it instructs the husband`, bodyHtml: `Free to <a href="https://fathersheartbible.com/read" style="color: var(--color-brand);" class="hover:underline">read online</a> with audio on every chapter, it’s built for a husband’s real week — come to be fathered before the alarm and the commute, and let the Word feed <em>you</em> so you have something to bring home.` },
