		{ question: `Is there a free online Bible with audio for husbands?`, answer: `Yes. The Father's Heart Bible™ is free to read and listen to online — no account, no purchase, no app. Open fathersheartbible.com/read on any phone or computer and read or hear any book, useful for a quick morning word, a verse for your marriage, or simply being fathered before the day begins.` },
		{ question: `What makes the Father's Heart Bible™ different for husbands?`, answer: `It is the first English translation to reveal God as Father wherever Scripture reveals Him as Father — so the love you're called to imitate has a Father's face. For husbands, that reframes everything: you come to the text first as a beloved son being loved, not only as a man trying to meet a standard, and you learn to love your wife from the overflow.` },
		{ question: `What does the Bible say about a husband providing for his family?`, answer: `Scripture honors a husband's care for his household, but it never makes a man's worth equal to his income. Galatians 4:7 calls you a son and heir; Matthew 6 says your Father knows what you need and clothes the fields in glory. Provision matters, but you are a son before you are a provider. The Father's Heart Bible™ lets you read these passages free, with audio, and rest your identity in your Father rather than your paycheck.` },
